             sworn. - I am a sadler, No. 3, Swallow-street; I bought this saddle and bridle of 
               <persName id="t18020428-57-person476">
                  John 
                  Bell
               <interp inst="t18020428-57-person476" type="surname" value="Bell"></interp>
