                  </persName>
            , on Wednesday, the 24th of March, about six o'clock in the evening; I gave him fifteen shillings for them; I knew him before when he was postilion, and afterwards coachman, to Sir 
               <persName id="t18020428-57-person477">
                  John 
                  Smith
               <interp inst="t18020428-57-person477" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
