             sworn. - I am an officer(produces the saddle) - I was sent for to apprehend the prisoner; I delivered the saddle and bridle to Lucas; I marked it first, and afterwards Lucas delivered it to me again.(The property was identified by Lucas.)</p>
               <p>Helder. This is the saddle and bridle that I bought of the prisoner; I marked them at the office.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I bought this saddle of a man in the street, who was going to Yorkshire for some horses from the country. <rs id="t18020428-57-verdict312" type="verdictDescription">
